Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.90,0:23:22.50,ED_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}趣味の違い　安心の相違が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.50,0:23:25.66,ED_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}君を戸惑わせても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:28.89,ED_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}私の道　形作るのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:32.54,ED_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}これだけ　Just LOVE or HATE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:27.67,ED_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}要是撩一下头发
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:30.91,ED_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}听到的会是喜欢还是讨厌？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:34.98,ED_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}随便吧 无论别人怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.98,0:22:37.92,ED_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}反正不会停下脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:41.70,ED_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}新闻的传播势不可挡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:44.42,ED_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}到了明天就忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:48.39,ED_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}所以今天比昨天好
